name: "WAGMI" (LoFi Cut)
description:
"WAGMI" is my 2nd official Ode to the NFT Community. As many know, the acronym stands for "We All Gonna Make It". This is a song of positive encouragement, uplifting energy, well regards & optimism for the NFT & crypto space.

This Music NFT is meant to be accessible across multiple chains in alternate versions. Each chain will have 2,000 editions! This Tezos version is the Lo-Fi cut.

Copyright is not transferred with ownership of this NFT. As a collector of this piece, you are free to share, play, & showcase this music art in all non-commercial settings or as part of a DJ set. Naturally, you are also free to resell on the secondary market. Ownership of this NFT does not provide collectors with rights to streaming royalties, but will cement you as an early patron of Mr. Wildenfree.

Word in the meteverse is... those who hold a Wildenfree NFT may find themselves in a better position for future releases, & may be randomly selected for special drops.

Peace & Blessings & cheers to you, for continuing to create, support, invest in, develop, & participate in this ever-expanding Metaverse. #WAGMI!

All the best,
Sean aka Mr. Wildenfree
